从小体育成绩好，身体柔软度也可以，所以配合运动没关系，但是请慢慢来…毕竟好几年没锻炼，现在就是个柔软度还不错的弱鸡… 好了，如果再有细节我忘记了，大家有疑问我再补充，请不要大意地，运动加美食谱地投入我爱的怀抱吧！ ---第一次修改的分割线--- 这是题主混知乎以来的处女帖啊！！！！！求玛丽苏汤姆苏大神庇护！！！！！ ---应该是最后一次修改的分割线--- 那个…犹豫好久觉得还是得出来说明一下… 我现在已经110了…从过年到现在1个多月看着看着就瘦下来了…呃…没怎么运动也没节食…只是吃饭不再添碗了…（对…我才发现我为什么长胖…是因为这半年在家…顿顿添碗…） 事实上…我彻底确认了我就是冬天会长肉，天气慢慢变暖我就慢慢瘦下来了的体质… 前几个月之所以会长肉长到我惊醒 是因为吃得太多加不动… 不好意思啊各位…"},"attached_info":"Cj0I7orq18nW/LYaEAMaBzcxMjczOTIgy7P8sQUwBTiqF0AUcggzNzMwMDkzNXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"148 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/e5cf2c83c6733edc46603340ccd80c4b.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"21_1623996466.5876062","card_id":"Q_275606514","target":{"id":275606514,"title":"怎么判断自己有没有城府？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/275606514","type":"question","created":1525243229,"answer_count":57,"follower_count":922,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[92348],"comment_count":5,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8I7orq18nW/LYaEAMaCDIzNTIxNjQxIN26pdcFMAU4mgdAFXIJMjc1NjA2NTE0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"139 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-423b116a82e4aeb5f17bf184f1d1b147_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"22_1623996466.5879543","card_id":"Q_465652857","target":{"id":465652857,"title":"2020 欧洲杯小组赛丹麦 1:2 比利时，如何评价这场比赛？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/465652857","type":"question","created":1623945418,"answer_count":29,"follower_count":41,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[2955,36667,169984,220767,403865],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"北京时间6月18日0:00，欧洲杯小组赛B组第二轮的一场较量，丹麦坐镇首都哥本哈